50
00:05:25.547 --> 00:05:26.997
The dream?

51
00:05:30.886 --> 00:05:33.253
You're my only dream.

52
00:05:33.305 --> 00:05:35.088
(chuckles softly)

53
00:05:38.593 --> 00:05:42.062
Will you ever
tell me what you see?

54
00:05:43.348 --> 00:05:46.232
