58
00:05:54.609 --> 00:05:57.444
Oh. but a beautiful cow it is.

59
00:05:57.496 --> 00:05:58.945
(laughing)

60
00:05:59.031 --> 00:06:01.614
(moos)

61
00:06:01.667 --> 00:06:03.416
Oh. he kicks fierce

62
00:06:03.452 --> 00:06:05.869
as his father
this morning.

63
00:06:05.954 --> 00:06:07.787
How do you know it's a he?

64
00:06:07.873 --> 00:06:09.289
Annora insists

65
00:06:09.341 --> 00:06:12.008
your firstborn will be an heir.

66
00:06:12.094 --> 00:06:14.377
Ah. we're taking divine council

67
00:06:14.463 --> 00:06:16.379
